  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TestNGEngineForGivenClientBasedModules

    public class TestNGEngineForDesiredSuites
extends AbstractTestNGEngine
    Purpose : is to execute the test scripts according to the module name provided by the user. Module name must be similar to the Suite xml file (child testng.xml) so this class will filter suites from the provided module name and execute filtered suites only. If no suite found then it will not execute any test scripts
